SectionBody.Text: The board shall by rule establish fees to be paid as follows:

Subsection.Text: Examination application fee, not to exceed $150;
Examination fee, not to exceed $175, which is refundable if the applicant is found to be ineligible to take the examination;
Initial licensure fee, not to exceed $600;
Trainee registration fee, not to exceed $100; and
Biennial renewal fee, not to exceed $600.
